---

---

<section
  class="first-section relative flex flex-col py-16 sm:py-24 md:py-32 xl:py-40 px-4 sm:px-6 md:px-16 bg-transparent"
>
  <!-- Fondo atmosférico -->
  <div class="absolute inset-0 z-0 pointer-events-none">
    <div
      class="absolute top-[-20%] left-[-15%] w-[60%] h-[80%] bg-[#02735e]/25 blur-[150px] rounded-full animate-drift-slow"
    >
    </div>
    <div
      class="absolute bottom-[-10%] right-[-10%] w-[50%] h-[60%] bg-[#d91414]/15 blur-[120px] rounded-full animate-drift-reverse"
    >
    </div>
    <div
      class="absolute top-[30%] left-[40%] w-[30%] h-[30%] bg-[#84d9d0]/15 blur-[100px] rounded-full animate-pulse-slow"
    >
    </div>
  </div>

  <div class="mx-auto max-w-[1400px] w-full relative z-10">
    <div class="flex flex-col items-start gap-8 sm:gap-10 md:gap-12 xl:gap-16">
      <!-- Logo arriba izquierda -->
      <div class="flex items-center gap-4 group">
        <div class="relative">
          <div
            class="absolute -inset-3 bg-[#84d9d0]/10 blur-xl rounded-full opacity-0 group-hover:opacity-100 transition-opacity duration-700"
          >
          </div>
          <img
            src="/CthulhuLanding/CTHULHU_LOGO_White_1920x1080.png"
            alt="Cthulhu: The Cosmic Abyss Logo"
            class="h-16 md:h-20 object-contain relative z-10 drop-shadow-[0_0_20px_rgba(132,217,208,0.4)] hover:drop-shadow-[0_0_35px_rgba(132,217,208,0.7)] transition-all duration-700"
          />
        </div>
        <!-- Línea decorativa tipo sonar -->
        <div
          class="flex-1 h-[1px] bg-gradient-to-r from-[#84d9d0]/40 via-[#02735e]/20 to-transparent max-w-xs"
        >
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- Título y texto centro -->
      <div class="w-full text-center flex flex-col items-center gap-6">
        <!-- Ornamento superior -->
        <div class="flex items-center gap-4 opacity-60">
          <div
            class="w-16 h-[1px] bg-gradient-to-r from-transparent to-[#84d9d0]/60"
          >
          </div>
          <svg
            width="18"
            height="18"
            viewBox="0 0 18 18"
            fill="none"
            class="text-[#84d9d0]/60"
          >
            <path
              d="M9 0L10.5 7.5L18 9L10.5 10.5L9 18L7.5 10.5L0 9L7.5 7.5Z"
              fill="currentColor"></path>
          </svg>
          <div
            class="w-16 h-[1px] bg-gradient-to-l from-transparent to-[#84d9d0]/60"
          >
          </div>
        </div>

        <h2
          class="text-3xl sm:text-4xl md:text-5xl lg:text-6xl xl:text-7xl font-black uppercase leading-[0.9] text-white tracking-wide max-w-4xl cthulhu-title"
        >
          Desciende hacia lo<br />
          <span
            class="text-transparent bg-clip-text bg-gradient-to-r from-[#84d9d0] via-[#02735e] to-[#84d9d0] animate-shimmer"
          >
            Desconocido
          </span>
        </h2>

        <p
          class="text-base sm:text-lg md:text-xl xl:text-2xl text-[#84d9d0]/70 font-light max-w-3xl leading-relaxed tracking-wide"
        >
          En el año 2053, la amenaza oculta se vuelve cada vez más evidente
          alrededor del mundo, mientras se multiplican los eventos extraños e
          inexplicables. A medida que los recursos de la superficie terrestre se
          agotan, <span class="text-[#84d9d0] font-medium"
            >poderosas corporaciones</span
          > se adentran en las profundidades inexploradas de los océanos, ignorando
          el horror ancestral que está a punto de despertar.
        </p>

        <!-- Ornamento inferior -->
        <div class="flex items-center gap-3 opacity-40">
          <div class="w-8 h-[1px] bg-[#84d9d0]/60"></div>
          <div class="w-2 h-2 rounded-full bg-[#84d9d0]/60"></div>
          <div class="w-8 h-[1px] bg-[#84d9d0]/60"></div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- Video -->
      <div class="w-full max-w-5xl mx-auto">
        <div
          class="video-wrapper aspect-video relative rounded-none overflow-hidden group"
        >
          <!-- Marco estilo BioShock/portilla submarina -->
          <div
            class="absolute -inset-[2px] bg-gradient-to-br from-[#84d9d0]/30 via-[#02735e]/20 to-[#d91414]/20 z-10 pointer-events-none"
          >
          </div>
          <div class="absolute inset-0 z-20 pointer-events-none">
            <!-- Esquinas ornamentales -->
            <div
              class="absolute top-0 left-0 w-12 h-12 border-t-2 border-l-2 border-[#84d9d0]/60"
            >
            </div>
            <div
              class="absolute top-0 right-0 w-12 h-12 border-t-2 border-r-2 border-[#84d9d0]/60"
            >
            </div>
            <div
              class="absolute bottom-0 left-0 w-12 h-12 border-b-2 border-l-2 border-[#84d9d0]/60"
            >
            </div>
            <div
              class="absolute bottom-0 right-0 w-12 h-12 border-b-2 border-r-2 border-[#84d9d0]/60"
            >
            </div>
            <!-- Scanlines encima del video -->
            <div
              class="absolute inset-0 bg-[linear-gradient(transparent_50%,rgba(0,13,12,0.06)_50%)] bg-[length:100%_3px] opacity-50"
            >
            </div>
            <!-- Glow hover -->
            <div
              class="absolute inset-0 shadow-[inset_0_0_60px_rgba(132,217,208,0.05)] group-hover:shadow-[inset_0_0_80px_rgba(132,217,208,0.12)] transition-all duration-1000"
            >
            </div>
          </div>
          <div
            class="absolute -inset-8 bg-[#84d9d0]/5 blur-[40px] opacity-0 group-hover:opacity-100 transition-opacity duration-1000 z-0"
          >
          </div>
          <video
            autoplay
            muted
            loop
            playsinline
            class="absolute inset-0 w-full h-full object-cover z-0"
          >
            <source
              src="/CthulhuLanding/CTHULHU_GAMEPLAY_OVERVIEW_4K_60fps_PRESS_UK_compressed_compressed.mp4"
              type="video/mp4"
            />
          </video>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>

  <!-- Botón Compra Ya -->
  <div class="relative z-10 flex justify-center pt-16 sm:pt-20 md:pt-28">
    <a href="#comprar" class="buy-btn group relative">
      <div
        class="absolute -inset-[1px] bg-gradient-to-r from-[#84d9d0]/0 via-[#84d9d0]/50 to-[#84d9d0]/0 opacity-0 group-hover:opacity-100 transition-opacity duration-500"
      >
      </div>
      <div
        class="relative border border-[#84d9d0]/30 bg-[#000d0c]/80 backdrop-blur-sm px-12 py-4 group-hover:border-[#84d9d0]/60 transition-all duration-500 overflow-hidden"
      >
        <div
          class="absolute inset-0 bg-[#84d9d0]/0 group-hover:bg-[#84d9d0]/5 transition-all duration-500"
        >
        </div>
        <div
          class="absolute inset-0 opacity-0 group-hover:opacity-100 bg-[linear-gradient(transparent_50%,rgba(132,217,208,0.05)_50%)] bg-[length:100%_3px] animate-interference"
        >
        </div>
        <span
          class="relative z-10 text-[#84d9d0]/60 group-hover:text-[#84d9d0] text-xs uppercase tracking-[0.5em] font-serif transition-all duration-300"
        >
          ◈ Compra Ya ◈
        </span>
      </div>
    </a>
  </div>
</section>

<style>
  .cthulhu-title {
    font-family: "Georgia", "Times New Roman", serif;
    text-shadow: 0 0 60px rgba(132, 217, 208, 0.15);
  }

  @keyframes drift-slow {
    0%,
    100% {
      transform: translate(0, 0) scale(1);
    }
    33% {
      transform: translate(3%, 5%) scale(1.05);
    }
    66% {
      transform: translate(-3%, 2%) scale(0.97);
    }
  }
  .animate-drift-slow {
    animation: drift-slow 20s ease-in-out infinite;
  }

  @keyframes drift-reverse {
    0%,
    100% {
      transform: translate(0, 0) scale(1);
    }
    33% {
      transform: translate(-4%, -3%) scale(1.04);
    }
    66% {
      transform: translate(2%, 4%) scale(0.98);
    }
  }
  .animate-drift-reverse {
    animation: drift-reverse 25s ease-in-out infinite;
  }

  @keyframes pulse-slow {
    0%,
    100% {
      opacity: 0.05;
      transform: scale(1);
    }
    50% {
      opacity: 0.12;
      transform: scale(1.2);
    }
  }
  .animate-pulse-slow {
    animation: pulse-slow 8s ease-in-out infinite;
  }

  @keyframes shimmer {
    0% {
      background-position: -200% center;
    }
    100% {
      background-position: 200% center;
    }
  }
  .animate-shimmer {
    background-size: 200% auto;
    animation: shimmer 6s linear infinite;
  }

  @keyframes interference {
    0% {
      background-position: 0 0;
    }
    100% {
      background-position: 0 100%;
    }
  }
  .animate-interference {
    animation: interference 0.3s infinite linear;
  }
</style>
